question: how many seconds in an hour
thoughts: To calculate the number of seconds in an hour, we can simply use the built-in Python time library and its constant for seconds in a minute (60) and minutes in an hour (60). Multiplying these two constants will give us the number of seconds in an hour.
answer_conversational: There are 3600 seconds in an hour.
